attributes.title: Roaches - TikTok Ban Revenge 🥰✨
attributes.review:
App was terrible. It crashed and once it did crash, roaches invaded my house as if they were looking for a roach King. And apparently they did because they then immediately entered my phone. I’m guessing the roach Queen was this app (Donald Trump)?? And not only that a Cheeto looking man came in my house and STOLE my microwave and oven, how else am I supposed to eat my delicious ramen noodles?! And once the app restarted and the roaches were gone, it literally blew up. As if this app was a detonation. I am currently writing this awful from my Grandmothers Samsung fridge- I had to drive an hour to write this!! Overall I don’t recommend the app as it has many problems, as well as the ones the other 1 star reviews claim it does. 🤦🏽‍♀️

Sincerely,
A Gen Z member
